id: pm-mnee
title: "Add pm stats --storage: aggregate history-stream metrics"
description: "No command surfaces per-stream sizes, line counts, or depth distribution; essential for deciding when to compact/redact and for storage planning."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: "area:history","area:storage",diagnostics,living-map
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:43:38.445Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-05T21:19:43.133Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: "Outputs total streams, lines, bytes, top-N by size/depth, oldest/newest entries; json+human; reuses drift cache where fresh (no full re-verify)."
value: "No command surfaces per-stream sizes, line counts, or depth distribution; essential for deciding when to compact/redact and for storage planning."
parent: pm-o2kc
resolution: "Shipped pm stats --storage via core/history/history-storage-stats.ts: total_streams/lines/bytes, largest_by_bytes + deepest_by_lines top-N, global oldest/newest entry. Reads streams once with no hash re-verification (lighter than the drift cache). The per-item 'pm history --stats' surface was folded into pm stats --storage since the aggregate belongs on stats."
